1. Install all the packages as mentioned in Pre-Requisite file. 
2. Download the script and save it in some local folder
3. Edit the script and enter the required details specific to user. 
4. Save the script and open Task Scheduler
5. Create a basic task to run the script multiple times a day 
6. Thats it! Make sure your system is on for it to work. 
7. You can also host the script on a server to remove the system dependency. 
8. For more, feel free to drop an email at ayushcrazx@gmail.com
